{"tid":2000227,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[蘋果ON FIRE]","createTime":"2020-05-03T17:07:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T17:09:22.000Z","uid":35562,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc853421149c2fb6cf8a2e8b15ba782d7743c97","tid":2000227,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"【#蘋果頭條】警隊多名高級洋警官近日被揭發住所非法僭建，他們的頂頭上司鄧炳強亦捲入僭建風波。本報調查發現，鄧炳強曾租住的九龍塘廣播道老牌豪宅寶能閣高層複式單位，天台一直存在違法僭建物，2017年初屋宇署已向業主發出清拆令，惟去年才遷出上址的鄧炳強，對此一直視若無睹，反而繼續享用400方呎非法豪裝天台。身兼九龍城區議員的律師黃國桐批評，雖然租客不須為僭建物負責，但身為執法人員卻不避嫌，租住並享受非法僭建帶來的好處，行為不檢點，觀感十分糟糕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">凌晨2點半登入蘋果日報網站/動新聞app，即可閱覽最新日報內容。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/95330061_10158954028817448_108356222377263104_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=Y0DV_tPA4FEAX-sYfX4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=c37f364dde6c23659c7630adea5a13ad&amp;oe=5ED44B3D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F95330061_10158954028817448_108356222377263104_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DY0DV_tPA4FEAX-sYfX4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3Dc37f364dde6c23659c7630adea5a13ad%26oe%3D5ED44B3D&h=49a2df66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19d22920cc96700a9df1fc853155a0529becbab4","tid":2000227,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:08:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收數佬有新地方聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"a026b4178ca80f053f4715baf6ad7e4ad18f57db","tid":2000227,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"痴撚線蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<